CONTENT:
Topic: Life as a student (describing one’s daily routine, strategies to study well
and be successful, choice of major and academic interests);
Listening activity;
Practical conversation activity;
Grammar focus: miscellaneous use of the present continuous.
EVALUATION:
Continued evaluation of in‑class activities.
OUTSIDE WORK:
Revision of vocabulary, expressions and dialogs.

