CONTENT:
Conversation topic: Vacation and Travel session (talking about one's traveling
experience);
Specific language functions covered: reminiscing about and promoting a
destination; asking about someone's travel experience;
Listening activity;
Practical conversations;
Applied grammar points: appropriate use of the Past Simple VS Present Perfect
– connecting ideas with "but", "or" and "so".
EVALUATION:
Continued evaluation of in‑class activities.
OUTSIDE WORK:
Revision of vocabulary, expressions and dialogs.

